git config --global user.name "liuyuqi"
git config --global user.email liuyuqi.crh@gmail.com
git config --global core.editor vim
git config --global merge.tool vimdiff

到项目所在根目录：git init
git clone https://github.com/.../.../....git

git status

添加一个文件：git add file
(add之前的更改才会被提交)

提交：git commit -m 'blablabla'
删除一个文件：git rm
取消改动：git checkout blabla.c  (该文件被复原至上一次提交的状态)

分支：git branch liuyuqi
删除分支：git branch -d liuyuqi
切换分支：git checkout liuyuqi
查看远程仓库：git remote -v
查看分支：git branch (-v)

提交到服务器：git push origin liuyuqi
pull: git pull origin liuyuqi(抓取远程数据并与本地数据合并)
fetch: git fetch origin (只从远程服务器抓取数据，并不与本地数据进行merge)
